Confluence Rest API Cheat Sheet

API to get the page id's
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content?type=page&start=0&limit=9999

API to get all the versions of page history
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/262187/version?expand=content

API to get content of a particular page with content ID 
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/262187?expand=space,body.view,version,container

API to get list of all spaces
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/space

API to get details about a specific space
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/space/Nitish/content/page?expand=history

API to List all pages in a space showing titles of page and IDs
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content?type=page&start=0&limit=99999

Api to get details of the current user viewing the page 
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user/current

Api to get page version details with body
https://nitish-dev.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content?spaceKey=NITISH&title=Nizhanth&expand=space,body.view,version,container
